data.description: Welcome home to 25410 Powerline Pass Drive! The charming front porch invites you into this beautifully maintained home with many lovely features. Formal dining room with attractive wood floors. Spacious living room with a gas fireplace is open the the kitchen. The delightful kitchen features plenty of granite counter space, storage, and a sunny breakfast nook with a window seat. First floor, spacious primary bedroom w/ bright ensuite bath/soaking tub/glass door shower and large walk-in closet. Upstairs features an inviting game room, and 3 spacious bedrooms. The living room and game room have wiring for surround sound. PEX plumbing throughout. Also wired for security.
